    "Poor simulation of fabric stiffness can make the avatar's clothing deform and swing more rigidegally when exercising, as well as causing unnatural mapping of clothing to different shapes of bodies.",
    "The accurate simulation of clothing fabrics in the Metaverse is another challenging topic.",
    "Issues of fashion copyright in Metaverse Digitization is a feature that makes it easy to replicate Metaverse fashion items, and it is reasonable to expect that the illegal copying and counterfeiting of fashion items will become more widespread in the Metaverse.",
